headline: Purpose Investments Inc. Announces November 2025 Distributions
summary: TORONTO, Nov. 18, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Purpose Investments Inc. (“Purpose”) is pleased to announce distributions for the month of November 2025 for its open-end exchange-traded funds and closed-end funds (“the Funds”). The ex-distribution date for all Open-End Funds is November 26, 2025. The ex-distribution date for all closed-end funds is November 28, 2025.
